title: National.Geographic.Naked.Science.Meltdown.WS.PDTV.XviD-BiQ.avi
description:
"Imagine a world where melting ice caps have raised sea levels by 20 feet and the great coastal cities of the world are under water. It is a nightmare scenario, but does it have a scientific basis? Discover the real science behind climate change."
Investigates the new science, suggesting that the IPCC report is based on old data and theory, and new findings show that a meltdown will be much sooner than expected.
